<type>Object</type>

<description><![CDATA[This is an unobtrusive table enhancement. It freezes the table's first row (or THEAD) and first column while the rest of the table is scrollable. If the table has a CAPTION it is removed and inserted above the frozen header.]]></description>

<syntax>new xTable(sTableId, sRoot, sCC, sFR, sFRI, sRCell, sFC, sFCI, sCCell, sTC, sCellT)</syntax>

<parameters>
  <par><name>sTableId</name><note><![CDATA[]]></note></par>
